Data Summary

The data were downloaded from 10X website https://support.10xgenomics.com/single-cell-gene-expression/datasets/1.3.0/1M_neurons. The original data includes 1,306,127 cells and 27,998 genes.

Sys.setenv(RETICULATE_PYTHON="/usr/bin/python3")
ad=import("anndata",convert = FALSE)
adata=ad$read_h5ad(filename)
adata=change_obs(adata,exclude=c("n_genes","n_counts"))

Supplementary Figure 16

df=getplotdata(adata,reduction.use = "tsne0.2")
df$desc_0.2=factor(as.numeric(as.character(df$desc_0.2)))
p1=getplot(df,by.group = "desc_0.2",pt.size=0.008)
